sequenceDiagram
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Serving
    participant CEConsumer as CloudEvent Consumer<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant RESTConsumer as Consumer Endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant KServeReconciler as KServe Payload<br/>Reconciler
    participant MMReconciler as ModelMesh Payload<br/>Reconciler
    participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>(PVC/MinIO/DB)
    participant Scheduler as Prometheus Scheduler<br/>(every 5s)
    participant Metrics as Fairness/Drift<br/>Calculators
    participant Publisher as Prometheus Publisher<br/>(Micrometer)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant ExplainerEP as Explainer Endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Core as Explainability Core<br/>(LIME/SHAP/CF)
    participant InferenceServer as KServe Inference<br/>Server

    Note over KServe,Storage: Flow 1: KServe CloudEvents Payload Ingestion
    KServe->>CEConsumer: CloudEvent (inference.request)<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    KServe->>CEConsumer: CloudEvent (inference.response)<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    CEConsumer->>KServeReconciler: Deserialize & match<br/>by correlation ID
    KServeReconciler->>Storage: Persist paired<br/>input+output dataframe row

    Note over ModelMesh,Storage: Flow 2: ModelMesh REST Payload Ingestion
    ModelMesh->>RESTConsumer: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    RESTConsumer->>MMReconciler: Deserialize & match<br/>by correlation ID
    Note over MMReconciler: Filter synthetic data<br/>(BIAS_IGNORE_PARAM)
    MMReconciler->>Storage: Persist paired<br/>input+output dataframe row

    Note over Scheduler,Prometheus: Flow 3: Scheduled Metric Calculation
    loop Every 5 seconds (configurable)
        Scheduler->>Storage: Read inference data<br/>(batch window)
        Scheduler->>Metrics: Calculate SPD, DIR,<br/>Meanshift, Fourier MMD
        Metrics-->>Scheduler: Metric values
        Scheduler->>Publisher: Publish as Micrometer gauges<br/>(trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir)
    end
    Prometheus->>Publisher: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>Bearer SA token
    Publisher-->>Prometheus: Prometheus text format

    Note over User,InferenceServer: Flow 4: On-Demand Explainability (disabled in RHOAI)
    User->>ExplainerEP: POST /explainers/local/lime<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    ExplainerEP->>Storage: Retrieve inference data
    Storage-->>ExplainerEP: Historical dataframe
    ExplainerEP->>InferenceServer: KServe v1/v2 HTTP or v2 gRPC<br/>Model inference calls
    InferenceServer-->>ExplainerEP: Prediction results
    ExplainerEP->>Core: Run LIME/SHAP/CF algorithm
    Core-->>ExplainerEP: Explanation result
    ExplainerEP-->>User: JSON explanation response
